name: Lucky In Love
description:
Posca on photo paper turned graphic turned NFT turned AR!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

this piece was inspired by a patch of four leaf clovers at my girlfriends apartment. we were heading to the pool and as she went inside to grab a few things before we walked over, I sat down on the curb and took out my markers. 


this piece is in collaboration with Killjoyink.tez who provided all the AR work, much help bringing this drawing to the digital space, and  giving the instructions on how to actually mint this piece. 

this piece will come with an exclusive airdrop from the Killjoyink.tez Genesis Collection <3 Check out @killjoyart club for more information on the collection <3
